        <item>
            <title>日本时兴超 cheap 100 円袋仔当银包，厚银包已经落伍，专家: 电子支付少带现金</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/japan-small-wallet/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-small-wallet</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/japan-small-wallet/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 11:16:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294684</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>科技日新月异，消费习惯随之变迁，钱包的使用风貌亦正悄然转型。日本一项调查透露，小型钱包渐成潮流，年轻人尤爱轻巧实惠之选，如 100 日元的杂志附赠品或三折设计。东京原宿 3 Coins 推出的 550 日元（约港币 29 元）钱包，以物美价廉之姿风靡市场，仅 1 个月内几近售罄，仅余黑色存货，足见其魅力。更有甚者，100 円商店的塑胶收纳袋摇身一变成为「钱包」，折射出世人对成本与实用的重新思量。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲东京原宿 3 Coins 推出的 550 日元钱包</p><h2>小型钱包何以乘势而起</h2><p>「小废包」盛行，钱包尺寸因势利导缩减。不少人为搭配轻便手袋，精心挑选袖珍钱包，仅置卡片与少量现金，简约中见巧思。智能手机支付普及，更令实体钱包退居幕后。渋谷 109 实验室所长一语道破：数码化洪流，如无现金交易与会员卡电子化，削弱钱包需求，「小废包」遂乘风而上。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲节目调查指因为手袋尺寸较小，所以改用更小的钱包</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小废包盛行</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家会特地选用更小的钱包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121-694x509.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121-694x509.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121.jpg 1026w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲渋谷 109 实验室所长长田麻衣表示因为电子支付盛行，现代人较少用现金，所以银包尺寸相应缩细</p><h2>「#100 均财布界隈」异军突起</h2><p>社交媒体上「#100 均财布界隈」声势浩大，意思是使用 100 円店的小型收纳袋代替钱包。渋谷街头一位 16 岁少女表示因屡失钱包，她转投卡通塑胶袋，经济实惠且无后顾之忧。另一名受访 50 岁市民则赞透明薄身设计一目了然，低调中不失实用。东京 100 円店员工笑言，小型收纳袋去年起销量节节上升，顾客别出心裁的用法教店方喜出望外。日本《朝日新闻》2024 年报导亦指出，100 円商店钱包销量持续攀升，彰显实用与价格并重的消费倾向。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「#100 均财布界隈」意思是使用百元商店的透明收纳袋充当银包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲受访少女表示自己经常丢失银包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲已经丢失过 3 次</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲因此使用用百元商店的透明收纳袋充当银包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲东京 100 円店员工表示没有想过收纳袋可以当银包用</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/japan-small-wallet/life-tech/epayment/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
