        <item>
            <title>Amazon AWS Ocelot 量子晶片亮相，内置纠错功能、成本降 90%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/amazon-web-services-announces-a-new-quantum-computing-chip/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=amazon-web-services-announces-a-new-quantum-computing-chip</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/amazon-web-services-announces-a-new-quantum-computing-chip/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 08:39:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Amazon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AWS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[量子电脑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294746</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Amazon Web Services (AWS) 宣布推出全新量子运算晶片 Ocelot。此晶片由加州理工学院的 AWS 量子计算中心团队研发，采用可扩展架构，与现行量子纠错方式相比，成本可降低多达 90%，加速实用量子电脑的应用开发。这项突破被视为建立容错量子电脑的重要一步，有望解决传统电脑无法应对的重大难题。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_70321"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CgcjHOS8e-M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Ocelot 晶片采用创新的设计，从基础层面内置纠错功能，并引入「猫量子位元」(cat qubit)。此技术以「薛丁格的猫」思想实验命名，能有效抑制特定错误，减少纠错所需的资源。AWS 成功将猫量子位元技术与其他纠错组件整合于微型晶片，并借鉴微电子业的成熟制程，实现可规模化生产。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294752" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740730244-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740730244-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740730244.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>AWS 量子硬件部门主管 Oskar Painter 表示：「随著近期量子研究的进展，实用容错量子电脑问世已不再是『是否』的问题，而是『何时』的问题，Ocelot 便是迈向这个目标的重要一步。未来，以 Ocelot 架构设计的量子晶片，所需的纠错资源将大幅减少，使其成本降至目前方法的五分之一。我们相信，这将加速实用量子电脑问世，最多可以提前五年。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294750" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1920x1080ocelot11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1920x1080ocelot11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1920x1080ocelot11.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Ocelot 虽为原型，但 AWS 预计其架构可将量子纠错成本降至现行方法的五分之一，缩短实用量子电脑开发时间最多 5 年。AWS 计划持续投入研发，并透过 Amazon Braket 服务推动量子技术进展。未来数年，业界竞争与技术突破将成为焦点。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
