            <title>长荣航空安全新规定  3 月起禁止航程中使用行动电源与备用锂电池</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/eva-flight-battery-ban/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=eva-flight-battery-ban</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/eva-flight-battery-ban/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 03:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
